  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483970/extras/f50b453b00755dc2532ab8fbd09d885b.poster.avif?t=1691099209\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483970/extras/f50b453b00755dc2532ab8fbd09d885b.webm?t=1691099209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483970/extras/f50b453b00755dc2532ab8fbd09d885b.mp4?t=1691099209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Welcome to \"Nullmaze\" - a world where you can buy items for collected coins to fill the world as you want and build your own adventure. Try different combinations of items, find the most powerful equipment, and become the reachest hero in history.<br><br><strong>Sandbox with your decisions</strong><br>You determine your game world by buying items that you want to be in your world!<br><br><strong>Complex combinations of items</strong><br>Open new game mechanics step-by-step: craft, level-up system, portals to new worlds!<br><br><strong>The game world is changing and built up of items you bought</strong><br>By getting coins you get new opportunities for the game world, from an empty piece of land it revolves into a world full of opportunities and dangers.<br><br>Find answers to the mysteries of this world and fight the legendary villain!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483970/extras/b6e82e3d4c5a941dca13b0260137a147.poster.avif?t=1691099209\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483970/extras/b6e82e3d4c5a941dca13b0260137a147.webm?t=1691099209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483970/extras/b6e82e3d4c5a941dca13b0260137a147.mp4?t=1691099209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483970/extras/f50b453b00755dc2532ab8fbd09d885b.poster.avif?t=1691099209\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483970/extras/f50b453b00755dc2532ab8fbd09d885b.webm?t=1691099209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483970/extras/f50b453b00755dc2532ab8fbd09d885b.mp4?t=1691099209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Welcome to \"Nullmaze\" - a world where you can buy items for collected coins to fill the world as you want and build your own adventure. Try different combinations of items, find the most powerful equipment, and become the reachest hero in history.<br><br><strong>Sandbox with your decisions</strong><br>You determine your game world by buying items that you want to be in your world!<br><br><strong>Complex combinations of items</strong><br>Open new game mechanics step-by-step: craft, level-up system, portals to new worlds!<br><br><strong>The game world is changing and built up of items you bought</strong><br>By getting coins you get new opportunities for the game world, from an empty piece of land it revolves into a world full of opportunities and dangers.<br><br>Find answers to the mysteries of this world and fight the legendary villain!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483970/extras/b6e82e3d4c5a941dca13b0260137a147.poster.avif?t=1691099209\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483970/extras/b6e82e3d4c5a941dca13b0260137a147.webm?t=1691099209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1483970/extras/b6e82e3d4c5a941dca13b0260137a147.mp4?t=1691099209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
